{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_10_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 song for you",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "——A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6666667,
          "startTime": 1.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いたいた。{user}さん\nちょっとこの、衣装デザイン案を見てほしいんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ there you are‚ {user}-san.\nCould you take a look at this costume design draft?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それはいいけど……\nなんで琴乃が、衣装デザインなんか描いてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ but…\nWhy are you the one drawing costume designs‚ Kotono?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それが、芽衣が「ライブで麻奈ちゃんの歌を歌うなら\nせっかくだしお揃いにしたら？」って言いだして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Mei said‚ “If you're going to sing Mana-chan's song at the live‚\nwhy not wear matching outfits too?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、遙子さんにバースデーライブのことを聞いて\n当時の衣装に近いデザインを考えてみてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I asked Haruko-san about the birthday live‚\nand tried coming up with a design close to the outfits back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4961918012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "すずにも「麻奈様の歌を歌うなら\n半端は許しませんわよ！」って言われちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu also told me‚ “If you're going to sing\nMana-sama's song‚ I won't allow any half-measures!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ言った手前、今日はボイスレッスンが終わったら\nすずも練習に付き合ってくれるみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ since she said that‚ after voice lessons today‚\nit looks like Suzu will help me practice too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんか、むしろ前よりオーバーワークになってないか？\nみんな、琴乃を見張ってるって言ってたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't this actually making you overwork more than before?\nI thought everyone said they'd be keeping an eye on you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "だ、大丈夫です。みんなわりと好き放題言ってますけど\nそれ以上に手伝ってくれてますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm fine. They all say what they like‚ but\nthey're helping me even more than that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "衣装デザインをやったことがないので、頭を抱えてたら\n千紗がかなり手を入れてくれましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I'd never done costume design before‚ when I was stuck‚\nChisa stepped in and helped me a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ついでに、沙季にお弁当を持たされました\n「どうせまた忘れるから先に用意しておきました」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Saki even handed me a lunchbox‚\nsaying‚ “You'll just forget again‚ so I prepared it in advance.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ただ渚が、お弁当箱にタコさんばっかり詰め込んで……\n確かに好きだけど、そればっかり食べたい訳じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Nagisa stuffed it completely full of octopus sausages…\nI do like them‚ but it's not like I want to eat only that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "白石姉妹はさすがだな……ついでに渚も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Shiraishi sisters sure are something… and Nagisa too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4371444148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなにいろいろアイデアももらいましたし\n当日はいいライブに出来そうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also got lots of ideas from everyone‚\nso it looks like we'll be able to make it a great live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに頼ってばっかりなので、お姉ちゃんには\nまだまだ半人前と言われるかもしれませんけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm relying on everyone so much‚\nmy sister might still call me inexperienced.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ならライブ当日は、月ストのみんながどれだけ凄いか\n麻奈に自慢するつもりで歌えばいいさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then on the day of the live‚ just sing like you're bragging to Mana\nabout how amazing Moon Tempest is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（きっと、麻奈は「知ってる」と言うと思うけど）\n（琴乃がそう報告することに、意味があるだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Though I'm sure Mana would just say‚ “I know.”）\n（But it's important that Kotono is the one telling her.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.866666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2104126377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ただし。楽しそうだし、手応えも感じてるみたいだから\nオーバーワークをしつこく止めはしないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That said‚ you look like you're enjoying yourself and feeling progress‚\nso I won't nag too much about overwork…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それでも無理し過ぎに見えたらストップはかけるからな\n沙季にもたまに報告を入れるように頼んでおく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if it still looks like too much‚ I'll stop you.\nI'll even ask Saki to report to me from time to time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……はい、気をつけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… okay‚ I'll be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0572381817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "——The day of the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.6333465576
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.6333465576
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.7000132243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、私にとっては特別な日なので\nちょっとだけ、姉の思い出話をさせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today is a special day for me‚\nso please allow me to share a little memory of my sister.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2557592554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "私は、姉がアイドルだった頃は\nまだ全然、こういう世界には縁がなかったので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when she was an idol‚\nI had no connection at all to this kind of world‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "姉がステージとかライブの話をするのを\n寂しく思いながら聞いていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so whenever she talked about stages and lives‚\nI listened‚ feeling lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.0935602032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "キラキラした芸能界の話を聞くたびに\n姉がどんどん遠くに行ってしまう気がして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each time I heard her stories about the glittering showbiz world‚\nI felt like she was going further and further away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.7780048533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私も今はアイドルとしてステージに立って……\nあの頃、姉がどんな景色を見ていたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But now‚ as I stand on stage as an idol myself‚\nI can finally see what scenery she was looking at back then‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてあんなに頑張っていたのか\nやっと分かるようになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and why she was working so hard.\nI finally understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.1878449285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに楽しくて、素敵な世界なら\n姉も夢中になるな、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In a world so joyful and full of wonder‚\nit makes sense that my sister was so absorbed in it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.4686841175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "今日は、その姉の誕生日なんです\nどうしても、姉にプレゼントを届けたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today is my sister's birthday.\nI really wanted to give her a present‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_jointstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "みんなにも手伝ってもらって、準備してきました\n良ければ、一緒にお祝いしてくれたら嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so with everyone's help‚ I prepared.\nIf you don't mind‚ I'd be happy if you celebrated with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、聴いて下さい――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now then‚ please listen—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.662997135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃん……あの時、ライブに行かなくてごめんね）\n（遅くなっちゃったけど、お誕生日おめでとう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sister… I'm sorry I didn't go to your live back then.）\n（It's late‚ but happy birthday.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんがいなくなって、寂しいけど）\n（でも大丈夫。私の周りにはみんながいてくれるから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I feel lonely with you gone‚ but…）\n（It's okay. I've got everyone around me now.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.8065746778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだか、胸が温かい……）\n（もしかしてお姉ちゃん、一緒に歌ってくれてるの？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Somehow‚ my heart feels warm…）\n（Could it be you're singing along with me‚ sister?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.5999796549,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "（なら、私ももっと頑張って歌わないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（If so‚ then I need to sing even harder.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.3352447508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんに負けないように……）\n（お姉ちゃんが、安心出来るように）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So I won't lose to you…）\n（So you can be at ease.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.6151657733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_03-ktn029.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃん、この歌が私からのプレゼントだよ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sister‚ this song is my present to you.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.1,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}